com.energyxxer.commodore.module

Class CommandModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.module.CommandModule

  • public class CommandModule
extends java.lang.Object
    The main agent of Commodore, storing data which is used by and for data packs, including, but not limited to, blocks, items, entities, functions, tags, etc. Command modules can be modified via other classes and compiled into data packs, which can then be used in Minecraft.
